additionalProperty.name: Ingredients
additionalProperty.value: Water, Sodium Hypochlorite, Non-ionic Surfactants, Sodium Hydroxide, Alkaline Salts, Chelating Agent

additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Do not mix with detergents or other chemicals. Hard surfaces bleach only. Not to be used on skin. For advice, contact a poisons information centre (phone Australia 131 126 and New Zealand 0800 764 766) or a doctor. If swallowed, do not induce vomiting. If in eyes, wash out immediately with water, hold eyelids apart and flush eyes continuously; flush until advised to stop by a poisons information centre or doctor, or for at least 15 minutes. If skin or hair contact occurs, remove contaminated clothing and flush skin and hair with running water.
